This package merges source code previously distributed as:

- yurunsoft/tdengine-restful-connector (MIT) — REST client under namespace Yurun\TDEngine\
- albertwill/tdengine-orm (MIT) — ORM under namespace Yurun\TDEngine\Orm\

Composer resolves Yurun\TDEngine\Orm\ before the shorter Yurun\TDEngine\ prefix.

Upstream references (for tracking updates): see repository README or release notes.
